      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Nobel RTV Export Pipeline\n\nTriggers RTV batch exports for Nobel Center Revit models,\nwaits for completion on the Windows Revit worker.\n\n## Triggers\n- **Schedule**: nightly at 00:30\n- **Webhook**: `POST /webhook/nobel-rtv-export`\n  - Body (optional): `{ \"batches\": [\"S2\", \"PL\"] }`\n  - Omit body to export all disciplines\n\n## Batch files\n`C:\\Users\\Nattugglan\\Nobel Center\\Syncpoint - General\\Pipeline\\RTV Config\\Batch\\`\n- PL-Batch.rbxml, S2-Batch.rbxml, SP1-Batch.rbxml\n- E1-Batch.rbxml, LA-Batch.rbxml, MEP-Batch.rbxml\n\n## Revit Worker\n- Location: `C:\\revit-worker`\n- Script: `C:\\revit-worker\\scripts\\Run-RTVXporterBatch.ps1`\n\n## IFC Output\nExported IFCs land in SharePoint:\n`Nobel Center\\Syncpoint - General\\Pipeline\\IFC-from-Revit`\n\nThe **Nobel Center Master Pipeline** (scheduled at 01:30)\npicks up new IFC files and runs post-processing + StreamBIM sync.",
